title: 779. Super Bowl Recap
itunes:title: 779. Super Bowl Recap
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys look at the first and second half of the Super Bowl between the Bengals and Rams. Next, the trio break down Rams wide receiver Cooper Kupp's Super Bowl MVP performance. Then, the guys focus on the Bengals final drive. To wrap up the show, the trio discuss what the Rams and Bengals need to do in the offseason to improve.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
